Class ConsoleReader

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable

    public class ConsoleReader
extends VeniceReader
    Receives input strings from console (transmitted by VeniceHub.java), converts them into TTE objects and put them into the TTEQueue. This class is for debugging purposes.
